&lt;p&gt;Are you a specialist in minor injury and minor illness management? Are you an experienced emergency practitioner (either Nurse or Allied Health Professional), with a passion for delivering exceptional patient focused care. Do you have level 6/7 minor illness and injury qualifications with proven experience and competence at band 6.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We now have opportunities for sessional Specialist Urgent Care Practitioners across our Minor Injury Units in Abingdon, Witney and Henley and GP Out of Hours bases in Abingdon, Witney, Banbury, Oxford and Bicester.&lt;/p&gt;
